Package: ecoDrift
Title: Model Change in Community Composition with Hubbell's Neutral Theory
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("James", "Saulsbury", , "jgsaulsbury@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Functions for fitting neutral (drift) models to timeseries of fossil
  community composition. Useful for measuring rates of ecological change, 
  fitting a variety of drift models to data, and visualizing relative abundances
  and fitted models.
